    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/764c74070a6e45a28f976f82673c669b.poster.avif?t=1755894426\" width=700 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/764c74070a6e45a28f976f82673c669b.webm?t=1755894426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/764c74070a6e45a28f976f82673c669b.mp4?t=1755894426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a young wizard, freshly graduated from the Academy and assigned to a remote coastal town with a troubled past. Though once a place of beauty, the town is now weighed down by lingering spirits, old conflicts, and creatures hiding in the mist. You’ve learned magic. Now, can you use it for something that truly matters?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/eeecacbbe72b5d537c9b59e0d22fad03.poster.avif?t=1755894426\" width=700 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/eeecacbbe72b5d537c9b59e0d22fad03.webm?t=1755894426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/eeecacbbe72b5d537c9b59e0d22fad03.mp4?t=1755894426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Begin</strong> as a Wizard Apprentice in the fallen town of Starfall, aiming to become the Archmage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Master</strong> 30+ wizard skills including potion-making, spellcasting, weapon crafting, summoning, elemental combat, rune crafting, and time manipulation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seek</strong> the 13 Lost Elementals hidden by the last Archmage in dangerous dungeons to restore peace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build</strong> a castle, marry one of datable NPCs, and share your home with creatures like alpacas and unicorns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/59c7a94c458c95b1f1119e35ec06d1bb.poster.avif?t=1755894426\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/59c7a94c458c95b1f1119e35ec06d1bb.webm?t=1755894426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/59c7a94c458c95b1f1119e35ec06d1bb.mp4?t=1755894426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fulfill</strong> requests from the townsfolk to help rebuild their lives.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run</strong> a Potion Shop, brewing potions from foraged ingredients.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Revive</strong> the town by running a Tavern, serving food, and training staff. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/2513eebf7339ebe906a29b07ac33fc5d.poster.avif?t=1755894426\" width=780 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/2513eebf7339ebe906a29b07ac33fc5d.webm?t=1755894426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/2513eebf7339ebe906a29b07ac33fc5d.mp4?t=1755894426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/9bb8001cc3a4d63d762752ee26643cbf.poster.avif?t=1755894426\" width=600 height=77 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195450/extras/9bb8001cc3a4d63d762752ee26643cbf.webm?t=1755894426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
